name: Sacho
description: $SACHO started as a joke — a cute little puppy memecoin meant for fun and memes. The devs left, but the community stayed, refusing to let it fade. They built websites, created memes, spread the word, and organized the roadmap. Under CTO Morty’s guidance, $SACHO grew from 8K to 16M, proving that a passionate community can turn a meme into a movement. Now at #4 on Dexscreener, the puppy is climbing fast, and this is only the beginning!
